data.name: txbMergeCMD.Text
data.value:
@ECHO OFF & TITLE 正在合并 - {文件名} PUSHD %~dp0
SET FCMD="{ffmpeg}" -allowed_extensions ALL -protocol_whitelist "file,crypto,http,https,tcp,tls" -report -loglevel +level+error -i "{本地TS列表.m3u8}" -c copy -bsf:a aac_adtstoasc "..\{文件名}.mp4" ECHO FFmpeg命令：%FCMD% %FCMD%
ECHO. ECHO FFmpeg退出码：ExitCode=%ERRORLEVEL% ECHO.
IF %ERRORLEVEL% EQU 0 ( CD .. RENAME "{文件名}" "OK.{文件名}" REM %SystemRoot%\Explorer.exe /e,/select,"{文件名}.mp4" ) ELSE PAUSE EXIT
